main.commit_message:
Add support for Python 3.11 and 3.12 and drop EOL 3.7

Mako 1.3.0 bumps the minimum Python version to 3.8, as 3.7 is EOL as of
2023-06-27.   Python 3.12 is now supported explicitly.
